#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rebuilds the KService desktop file system configuration cache"
msgstr ""
"Ponovno zgradi konfiguracijski predpomnilnik datotečnega sistema namizja "
"KService"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synopsis"
msgstr "Povzetek"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> <group choice=\"opt\" rep=\"repeat"
"\"><replaceable class=\"option\">OPTIONS</replaceable></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> <group choice=\"opt\" rep=\"repeat"
"\"><replaceable class=\"option\">MOŽNOSTI</replaceable></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> builds binary cache of the data stored in "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> and &MIME; type <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal> files that the KService framework uses to find "
"plugins, applications and other services."
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> zgradi binarni predpomnilnik podatkov "
"shranjenih v <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> in vrsti datotek "
"&MIME; <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal>, ki jih ogrodje KService "
"uporablja za iskanje vtičnikov, aplikacij in drugih storitev."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The KService library uses this database to efficiently provide the "
"information requested of it."
msgstr ""
"Knjižice KService uporablja to podatkovno bazo, da učinkovito zagotovi "
"informacije, ki so od nje zahtevane."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Users do not normally need to run this application directly; KService will "
"run it if necessary, when any of the files whose data is cached are changed."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnikom ponavadi ni potrebno neposredno zaganjati te aplikacije; če je "
"to potrebno, jo KService zažene sam, ko je spremenjena katerakoli datoteka, "
"katere podatki so v predpomnilniku."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Možnosti"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "--global"
msgstr "--global"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ignores any user-set files (in <varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</varname>). This is "
"currently only supported on &UNIX; systems."
msgstr ""
"Prezre vse datoteke, ki jih je nastavil uporabnik (v <varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</"
"varname>). Ta lastnost je trenutno podprta le na sistemih &UNIX;."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "--noincremental"
msgstr "--noincremental"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rather than using the existing cache and only updating the information that "
"has changed or been added, start with an empty cache. Ignored if <option>--"
"global</option> is set."
msgstr ""
"Namesto da se uporablja obstoječi predpomnilnik in posodablja le "
"informacije, ki so bile spremenjene ali dodane, začni raje s praznim "
"predpomnilnikom. Prezrto, če je nastavljen <option>--global</option>."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "--menutest"
msgstr "--menutest"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Test the generation of the application menu database. Does not actually "
"build the cache."
msgstr ""
"Preizkusi generacijo podatkovne baze aplikacijskega menija. Dejansko ne "
"zgradi predpomnilnika."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "--testmode"
msgstr "--testmode"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the QStandardPaths \"test mode\" to avoid interfering with user data. "
"This is intended for use with unit tests."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi \"način testiranja\" QStandardPaths, da ne pride do posega v "
"podatke. Namenjeno uporabi s testnimi enotami."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "--track <replaceable>menu-id</replaceable>"
msgstr "--track <replaceable>id-menija</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track a menu ID for debugging."
msgstr "Sledi ID menija z namenom razhroščevanja."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "--author"
msgstr "--author"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show author information."
msgstr "Prikaži informacije o avtorju."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "--license"
msgstr "--licence"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show license information."
msgstr "Prikaži informacije o licenci."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h, --help"
msgstr "-h, --help"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show a brief help text."
msgstr "Prikaži kratko besedilo pomoči."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v , --version"
msgstr "-v , --version"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show version information."
msgstr "Prikaži informacije o verziji."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Files"
msgstr "Datoteke"

#. Tag: filename
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<varname>cachedir</varname>/ksycoca6_[lang]_[sha1-of-dirs]"
msgstr "<varname>cachedir</varname>/ksycoca6_[lang]_[sha1-of-dirs]"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The KService cache generated by <command>kbuildsycoca6</command>. On &UNIX; "
"systems, <varname>cachedir</varname> is typically <filename class=\"directory"
"\"><envar>XDG_CACHE_HOME</envar></filename>."
msgstr ""
"Predpomnilnik KService je ustvarjen z <command>kbuildsycoca6</command>. Na "
"sistemih &UNIX; je <varname>cachedir</varname> ponavadi <filename class="
"\"directory\"><envar>XDG_CACHE_HOME</envar></filename>."

